<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Filigree on RaihnForge</title><link>https://RaihnForge.github.io/tags/filigree/</link><description>Recent content in Filigree on RaihnForge</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Thu, 21 Apr 2011 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://RaihnForge.github.io/tags/filigree/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Wedding Invitations</title><link>https://RaihnForge.github.io/art/branding/wedding-invitations/</link><pubDate>Thu, 21 Apr 2011 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://RaihnForge.github.io/art/branding/wedding-invitations/</guid><description>&lt;p>&lt;a href="http://www.joshuakeyes.us/wordpress/raihn/images/Wedding-Invitations_D253/wedding_invite_blog-post.jpg">&lt;img src="http://www.joshuakeyes.us/wordpress/raihn/images/Wedding-Invitations_D253/wedding_invite_blog-post_thumb.jpg" alt="wedding_invite_blog post" title="wedding_invite_blog post">&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>I created these invites for my best friend’s wedding.  Working with the bride to be we designed some fun invitations to send out.  The original color for them was yellow, but its difficult to get the correct yellow to display on monitors throughout the web, so I changed up the color to blue for this blog post.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;a href="http://www.joshuakeyes.us/wordpress/raihn/images/Wedding-Invitations_D253/invite_front_blogpost.jpg">&lt;img src="http://www.joshuakeyes.us/wordpress/raihn/images/Wedding-Invitations_D253/invite_front_blogpost_thumb.jpg" alt="invite_front_blogpost" title="invite_front_blogpost">&lt;/a>&lt;a href="https://RaihnForge.github.io/images/recovered/invite_back_blogpost.jpg">&lt;img src="https://RaihnForge.github.io/images/recovered/invite_back_blogpost.jpg" alt="invite_back_blogpost" title="invite_back_blogpost">&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;a href="http://www.joshuakeyes.us/wordpress/raihn/images/Wedding-Invitations_D253/rsvp_blogpost.jpg">&lt;img src="http://www.joshuakeyes.us/wordpress/raihn/images/Wedding-Invitations_D253/rsvp_blogpost_thumb.jpg" alt="rsvp_blogpost" title="rsvp_blogpost">&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>I enjoyed working with my friends on this project.  My favorite part was creating the filigree-like sketches for the floral designs on the corners of the composition.  I hope you enjoyed the invitations! &lt;img src="http://www.joshuakeyes.us/wordpress/raihn/images/Wedding-Invitations_D253/wlEmoticon-openmouthedsmile.png" alt="Open-mouthed smile">&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>